Input:
Path: /admin/download?file=/var/log/app.log
Status: 200
Size: 145230
Response snippet: [ERROR] Login failed for user admin@corp.com from 192.168.1.5\n[INFO] DB query: SELECT * FROM users WHERE

Output:
{
  "finding": "/admin/download?file=/var/log/app.log",
  "severity": "high",
  "worth_reporting": true,
  "title": "Arbitrary File Read via Download Parameter",
  "description": "The download endpoint accepts a file parameter that reads arbitrary files from the server filesystem. Log files containing sensitive data are accessible.",
  "impact": "Internal log access reveals user emails, internal IPs, SQL queries, and application internals",
  "steps": ["GET /admin/download?file=/var/log/app.log", "Response contains internal log data", "Escalate: try ?file=/etc/passwd, ?file=../../../wp-config.php"],
  "notes": "Test for full LFI escalation — this is likely a path traversal entry point"
}

